column2: select * from optw.tamass.VARIABLES where UNIT=&&& and CONCEPT like &&&) select Commute=REPLACE(MIN(b.label),&&&,&&&), N=sum(v.VAL) from optw.tamass.VALS v     join bins b on b.ID=v.VARID where TRACTID in (      select TRACTID from optw.tamass.TRACTS      where vintage = #         and geom.STArea() < #e9 -- m^# -- excluding huge tracts         and geom.STDistance(@center) < # / SQRT(#) * # -- meters ) group by VARID order by VARID asc
